## 3. Commercial Use Terms

If you use or distribute the Software (or any derivative work of it) in conjunction with a Dependent Component that does **not** qualify as Free Distribution, the following terms apply:

- You must obtain a **commercial license** from the author.
- You must **report all distributions or sales** of the Dependent Component that includes or uses the Software.
- You must **provide access to the email addresses** of users who download or purchase the Dependent Component.
- You agree to **pay a per-installation or per-sale fee**, as separately agreed with the author.

These requirements apply whether the Software is bundled with, integrated into, or merely used by the Dependent Component.

## 4. Plugin Use in Articles

The included plugin enabling article-based checkout functionality is part of the Software and is subject to the same licensing terms.

